{"type": "article", "id": 26289, "title": "皮革背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162628PinXdDmbo5ORvUNZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这个散发着复刻质感的皮革包名为 Leather Ruck Sack，是美国阿拉巴马州独立品牌 <a href=\"http://loyalstricklin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Loyal Stricklin</a> 的一款产品。背包由植鞣真皮制作而成，坚固耐重的同时，恰到好处的褶皱为背包增添了时尚感，好像是电影中出现的户外探险家的装备。无论是打算来一场旅行还是想为日常生活增添一股户外风，都很合适。你可以通过<a href=\"http://loyalstricklin.com/products/leather-ruck-sack-light-tan\">预定链接</a>了解它的详细规格，售价为 750 美元，需要花费两周时间制作。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162624hA8N3pRwDgoP5r0B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162625FfjPWTky2Hi0b1L9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162626TmYBVArylCtPqWw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216262696owixD47CIfQW31.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}